  "texts": [
    "In the experiment in Chapter 4, we set K to 2.",
    "In this section, we set K to 1 as a comparative experiment.",
    "Because of the length limit of BERT input, when K = 3 or greater, our input will be truncated in most cases, so that context cannot complete the input into BERT.We show the results in Fig. 3.",
    "We observed that: (1) Increasing or decreasing the length of the keyword list negatively impacts the model's performance.",
    "When the length is 3, the model achieves the best performance."
